com.emiliano.fmframework.core

Class Feature<SoftElement>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.emiliano.fmframework.core.Feature<SoftElement>
  • Type Parameters:
    SoftElement - the generic type

    public class Feature<SoftElement>
extends java.lang.Object
    The class Feature represents a selectable element of a model. A feature is compound by an identifier name, an optional set of attributes (each attribute with a name and Object value), and an optional FeatureAction. element.
